entry.title: Russian Missiles Stretch Ukraine's Air Defenses
entry.content: Russia launched a barrage of missiles and drones against Kyiv and other Ukrainian cities, continuing its recent effort to deplete Ukraine’s air defenses ahead of the country’s planned offensive.

entry.title: Persian Gulf States Boom With Billionaires, Beyoncé and Bling
entry.content: Oil-rich Gulf countries have become a magnet for global wealth, and they’re trying new strategies to keep the good times rolling.

entry.title: World's Biggest Tourism Spenders Aren't Traveling---And May Not for Years
entry.content: Limited flights and other bottlenecks are keeping many Chinese from venturing abroad, depriving the world of needed spending.
